<cb:div type="nanchuan-notes">
<head>漢譯南傳大藏經 註解</head>
<p>
<note n="0145001" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0145001">依異本 Puḷinaṁ，又可讀為 Pūḷinaṁ。</note>
<note n="0145002" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0145002">asītikappe 訂正為 nantayaso。</note>
<note n="0147001" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0147001">cakkavāka 好聲鳥，印度郭公鳥。</note>
<note n="0147002" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0147002">sevāla 草之名。</note>
<note n="0147003" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0147003">Sucārudassana（善愛見）。</note>
<note n="0148001" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0148001">讀為 Sena（異本）。</note>
<note n="0148002" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0148002">Uggata（昇）。</note>
<note n="0149001" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0149001">Vessabhū 為過去七佛之第三佛，故此有諸仙中第三之稱。</note>
<note n="0149002" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0149002">Samodhāna（並置）。</note>
<note n="0150001" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0150001">Dīghāyu（長壽）。</note>
<note n="0151001" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0151001">Aruṇaka（太陽）。</note>
<note n="0152001" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0152001">讀為 damathenāhaṁ（異本）。</note>
<note n="0153002" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0153002">Ambatthaja（菴婆核生）。</note>
<note n="0153001" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0153001">讀為 cattārasa（異本）。</note>
<note n="0154001" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0154001">Anojā 為開赤花之灌木。</note>
<note n="0154002" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0154002">Devabhūti（神現）。</note>
<note n="0155001" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0155001">原文雖為 Addhāpupphi，今採異本為 Avopupphi。暹羅本則為 atho Pupphi。</note>
<note n="0155002" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0155002">Paccā〔bhi〕gamana。</note>
</p>
</cb:div>
</back></text></TEI>